des: Tre’ Rochelle is celebrating through birthday trivia and song, urban soul music artists ( singers & musicians ) of today and yesterday that have created music that stirred our souls. Can you guess who’s birthday is today? Tune in everyday to hear if you can guess our Urban Soul Music Birthday Stars for the day!
